nqubits = 1
p = Program('Butterfly', platf, nqubits)
k = Kernel('0', platf, nqubits)
k.prepz(0)
k.measure(0)
k.measure(0)
k.measure(0)
p.add_kernel(k)
k = Kernel('1', platf, nqubits)
k.prepz(0)
k.measure(0)
k.x(0)
k.measure(0)
k.measure(0)
p.add_kernel(k)
p.compile()
QISA_fn = os.path.join(output_dir, p.name + '.qisa')
assemble(QISA_fn)
